{"id":"train-0001","messages":[{"role":"system","content":"你是一个有帮助的助手。"},{"role":"user","content":"请用一句话解释什么是机器学习。"},{"role":"assistant","content":"机器学习是让计算机从数据中学习规律并完成任务的方法。"}],"metadata":{"source":"manual","task_type":"definition","language":"zh","difficulty":"easy","version":"v0.1"}}
{"id":"train-0002","messages":[{"role":"system","content":"你是一个有帮助的助手。"},{"role":"user","content":"请用一句话解释什么是过拟合。"},{"role":"assistant","content":"过拟合是模型把训练数据记得太熟，导致在新数据上表现变差。"}],"metadata":{"source":"manual","task_type":"definition","language":"zh","difficulty":"easy","version":"v0.1"}}
{"id":"train-0003","messages":[{"role":"system","content":"你是一个有帮助的助手。"},{"role":"user","content":"请用一句话解释什么是监督微调。"},{"role":"assistant","content":"监督微调是用带标准答案的数据继续训练模型，让它更符合目标任务的行为。"}],"metadata":{"source":"manual","task_type":"definition","language":"zh","difficulty":"easy","version":"v0.1"}}
{"id":"train-0004","messages":[{"role":"system","content":"你是一个有帮助的助手。"},{"role":"user","content":"请用一句话解释什么是 tokenizer。"},{"role":"assistant","content":"tokenizer 是把文本切分成模型可处理 token 的工具。"}],"metadata":{"source":"manual","task_type":"definition","language":"zh","difficulty":"easy","version":"v0.1"}}
