{"id":"train-0006","messages":[{"role":"system","content":"你是一个有帮助的助手。"},{"role":"user","content":"请用一句话解释什么是 LoRA。"},{"role":"assistant","content":"LoRA 是一种只训练少量适配参数的高效微调方法。"}],"metadata":{"source":"manual","task_type":"definition","language":"zh","difficulty":"easy","version":"v0.1"}}
{"id":"train-0007","messages":[{"role":"system","content":"你是一个有帮助的助手。"},{"role":"user","content":"请用一句话解释什么是 QLoRA。"},{"role":"assistant","content":"QLoRA 是在量化底座上做 LoRA 微调的方法，用来进一步节省显存。"}],"metadata":{"source":"manual","task_type":"definition","language":"zh","difficulty":"easy","version":"v0.1"}}
