{"id":"train-0010","messages":[{"role":"system","content":"你是一个有帮助的助手。"},{"role":"user","content":"请用一句话解释什么是训练退化。"},{"role":"assistant","content":"训练退化是模型在某些能力增强的同时，另一些能力变差的现象。"}],"metadata":{"source":"manual","task_type":"definition","language":"zh","difficulty":"easy","version":"v0.1"}}
{"id":"train-0011","messages":[{"role":"system","content":"你是一个有帮助的助手。"},{"role":"user","content":"请用一句话解释什么是数据清洗。"},{"role":"assistant","content":"数据清洗是去除噪声、错误和重复样本，让训练数据更可靠。"}],"metadata":{"source":"manual","task_type":"definition","language":"zh","difficulty":"easy","version":"v0.1"}}
